	<td align="left">
		<span class="path" style="color:#cccccc">Persistent URL :</span>&nbsp;<a href="http://dlib.eastview.com.ezproxy.stanford.edu/browse/doc/5732430" class="path" style="color:#cccccc">http://dlib.eastview.com/browse/doc/5732430</a>
